## Feature Flag

### `user_limits.use_code_engine` (boolean, default `false`)

- `false` = All traffic routes to n8n (current behavior, unchanged)
- `true` = All traffic routes to Code Engine

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Default is `false` for EVERYONE** — existing users, new signups, all of them. You manually flip it to `true` on your test account. Once verified, we change the DB default to `true`.

